  "keyFeatures": [
    "Parse Fortnite replay files with multiple parse modes (Minimal, Normal, Full)",
    "Extract comprehensive game data including players, eliminations, stats, and events",
    "Support for encrypted replay files with automatic decryption",
    "High-performance parsing with configurable settings to ignore unnecessary data",
    "Detailed player tracking including locations, inventory, health, and weapon switches",
    "Game event extraction (eliminations, match stats, team stats, safe zones)",
